(Study Tips After Reading) Tj
T*
(- Rewrite the overview of Summary in your own words after studying it.) Tj
T*
(- Use short exercises built around shortening passages into key points before trying) Tj
T*
(harder tasks.) Tj
T*
(- Keep track of mistakes such as copying large parts of the original text and write the) Tj
T*
(correction beside each one.) Tj
T*
